{
  "stem": "7069.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Because he could tell whom he had in front of him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he took him down in the basement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next day the farmer came to him and he said, say, do you-- were you with another group of about 52 prisoners?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my brother said, oh yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, well, he says, then you are lucky that you came here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because these 52 prisoners were all put before a machine gun, and all shot over-- all shot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is the way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, under these circumstances, the condition that I was, there would have been no chance for both of us to survive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you see, sometimes in life, the thing that you think is the worst that happens to you turns out to be a-- a lucky break.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As it turns out then, when my brother was taken away from me, I-- This is an incredible-- incredible story.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I will tell that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It will take a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now my brother was away from me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took inventory of my situation very, very clearly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time I knew I had no chance, unless I do something drastic, which I hope will work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And our blockalteste, the commander of the barrack, so to speak, happened to be, in this particular case, a man who hated Jews with a fashion.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a man from the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not trying to say that Ukrainians are all hating Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A good number do, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then there are also some wonderful Ukrainians, even known, nowadays, that actually helped Jews, so-- But this man hated Jews with a fashion.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Any time he had a chance, he would-- would beat up on us, would beat people to a pulp, prisoners to a pulp.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
